{"id":"13819","title":"神仙眼","writer":"全市虾蟹","dateline":"1437172075","updatetime":"1437172075","isover":"1","filesize":"2425629","linecount":"25097","wordcount":"768701","imgpath":"https://photos.smugmug.com/photos/i-hTMHQVr/0/0dc5f42e/Th/i-hTMHQVr-Th.jpg","hash":"shenxianyan","urlhash":"","sign":"","desc":"穷小子叶欢机缘巧合的拥有了当年太上老君炼丹炉里孙悟空火眼金睛的灵识。\n书画，陶瓷，器皿，赌石之类的都是都市那些拥有普通异能者发财干的事情，咱这是神眼，不能老是去抢那些人的饭碗啊，要不，那些人不是又得穷死。\n咱应该要去发掘那些翡翠矿，钻石矿啥的......传世翡翠要收回，被称为钻石中稀世奇珍，品级最高的红钻这要。文房四宝也喜欢，家里书桌上就按照当年乾隆爷用的摆一套。\n领导人需要我帮他治病？没说的，给几个中央警卫局的特种兵当保镖应该行吧。倭国的也要我帮忙？没关系，国际友人嘛，给几个元青花那些坛坛罐罐的就行。实在没有，唐伯虎的画给两张也成。\n米国也需要帮助？简单，一架阿帕奇，两辆悍马。这不过份吧？先说好了，咱要的是军用悍马，最起码能抵挡AK扫射一阵子的，别给我那民用版的，要是开着那些个垃圾上路给哥几个知道了得笑死，咱跌不起那份......","hot":"189","num":"20200","cid":"73","suggcate":"现代都市,都市异能","suggcids":"215","notbook":"0","fetchv":"0","lasthot":"1477682214","clicknum":"83","isvip":"0","ish":"0","age":"现代","channel":"男","isqiniu":"1","list":"0,39n,74x,ay0,efx,ica,m4o,poc,t5c,wew,105x,144t,17qg,1b6a,1epn,1i1o,1l2z,1og8,1ral,1uim,1xhm,20m2,23pf,27jy,2bet,2ekm,2i9l,2luz,2psi,2t2g,2w8y,30ko,3416,37zc,3bq9,3frf,3jh5,3n5u,3qp7,3u4y,3x28,40b5,43qt,46sf,4amr,4dj3,4gzi,4k0k,4nf1,4qvw,4tsl,4xgv,50yc,541f,57gu,5aw4,5ed9,5i15,5l0h,5o57,5rhx,5uug,5ycp,61pj,65ez,68ei,6b9c,6em0,6i2t,6l9w,6o2u,6r40,6ukt,6xrf,71ku,74p2,786p,7bfx,7er7,7hyo,7lkn,7o7c,7rif,7v6m,7ycf,81kx,85w4,89zd,8dln,8hki,8l62,8oja,8rpj,8vct,8yjm,921l,95uv,99on,9dov,9grs,9k12,9ns9,9r0t,9ud5,9xev,a1ht,a51z,a886,ac76,aexr,aj1o,amea,apvg,ateg,axff,b0zs,b5by,b8y5,bcnx,bgjf,bk62,bnfu,brkv,bum7,byvd,c2lv,c6vw,cad3,cdyy,ch51,clgs,cprh,ctji,cx6h,d0wy,d4o4,d98n,ddev,dh2t,dlbt,doh6,dscg,dvjh,dzjo,e3rh,e83b,ebs7,eg59,ejdd,emlc,eplh,et71,ewf0,ezl2,f26y,f5it,f8ii,fccw,fg15,fjuu,fneo,fqup,fug1,fxpq,g0jd,g3np,g714,gafr,gdr9,ggq4,gkk8,go4y,grwu,gv9j,gzjs,h3qd,h7ic,hao4,hdyb,hhxa,hlyi,hqag,htdh,hww6,i04a,i47j,i80d,ic08,ig00,iko0,ioid,is4j,iwih,j12b,j60c,j9vi,jdvx,jhlw,jkkp,jnvs,jrg0,jut1,jz0z,k2yk,k6wy,kb0m,kfaz,kjnk,knq7,krot,kvnb,kzv8,l3s3,l7k9,lblt,lghm,ll05,loql,lswx,lxn3,m28d,m7zk,mcnh,